      ************************************************************
      *  *IN20:1(NOT READ FGBPL01:DETAIL CODE MANAGEMENT)        *
      *  *IN21:1(NOT READ AFCPL90:ORDER FILE)                    *
      *  *IN30:1(NOT EXIST IZAPL01:MATERIAL KANBAN)              *
      *  *IN31:1(NOT READ IZAPL01:MATERIAL KANBAN)               *
      ************************************************** AFCR90 **
     FAFCPW90 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FFGBPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FIZAPL02 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAFCPL80 UF  E           K        DISK
     FAFCPL90 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FAFCNP90 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     E                    ER      1   4 60
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80C8SKHZ
     I                                        1   40C8SKYY
     I                                        5   60C8SKMM
     I                                        7   80C8SKDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80C8KOHZ
     I                                        1   40C8KOYY
     I                                        5   60C8KOMM
